name: DataBeasts Forest
description:
A fan art piece that was made to try to win Databeast #51 in a raffle. Lala finds herself meeting some databeasts from the local forest. Featuring Lala #2, Honey #7, Radhi #8, Blum #9. 
Inspired by the concept work from Pikmin 2, I wanted visualize some of the designs in a real world setting.
